$PROBLEM 002 Growth Dynamics Model (Wang model) ; Executed By: shellyw ; Date: Thu Aug 16 13:53:22 EDT 2018 ; NONMEM Version: 7.4.0 ; DESCRIPTION: W-TGD model, 3-pop mixture on (TB0, TG, TS), tx~(TG,TS),LINE~(TG,TS), TG3=0 and plateu limit
; DESCRIPTION: METHOD=FOCE
; DATASET:
; RESPONSEVA: SLD
; DESCRPIIV: (TB0,TG,TS), TLIM, same subpop IIV
; DESCRPIOV: none
; RESERR: Additive
; COVMODEL: none $INPUT C STUDY=DROP STUDN USUBJID=DROP ID AFlagN CMT EVID TIME DV TIME130 DV130 Treatment=DROP TRTN TXN TXAN SEX KPSN MSKN NILSN PDL11N PDL15N LINEN BBWT cBBWT lBBWT lcBBWT BALB cBALB lBALB lcBALB AGE BSLD lcBSLD lcBMLD IBALB=DROP ITX=DROP IKPS=DROP IMSK=DROP NEWLF NEWLFT Nobs FOBST CAVG1 ICAVG1 MDV DROP
$DATA ../../../data/derived/jointData_26Nov2018.csv IGNORE=C IGNORE=(TXN==99,CMT==2, AFlagN==2, AFlagN==3)
;TXN (99, missing treatment values)
$CONTR OBSDATA=(TXAN)
$ESTIMATION MAX=9999 PRINT=5 METHOD=1 NSIG=3 SIGL=10 MSFO=./002.msf $COVARIANCE MATRIX=R PRINT=E UNCONDITIONAL $PRED
INILSN = NILSN
; Specify symbolic vars for fixed effects params TVTB0 = THETA(1) ; typical baseline tumor burden [cm] TVTG = THETA(2) ; typical tumor growth rate [cm/week] TVTS = THETA(3) ; typical tumor shrinkage rate [1/week]
; Specify symbolic vars for residual error std.dev AERR = THETA(4) PERR = THETA(5)
; Specify symbolic vars for ETAs ZTB0 = ETA(1) ZTG = ETA(2) ZTS = ETA(3)
ZTLIM = ETA(4)
TLIM = 0
; Modify params for mixture sub-pop 2 IF(MIXNUM .EQ. 2) THEN TVTB0= THETA(6) ; typical baseline tumor burden [cm] TVTG = THETA(7) ; typical tumor growth rate [cm/week] TVTS = THETA(8) ; typical tumor shrinkage rate [1/week] ;ZTB0 = ETA(4) ;ZTG = ETA(5) ;ZTS = ETA(6) ENDIF
IF (MIXNUM.EQ.3) THEN TVTB0 = THETA(9) ; typical baseline tumor burden [cm] TVTG = THETA(10) ; typical tumor growth rate [cm/week] TVTS = THETA(11) ; typical tumor shrinkage rate [1/week] ;ZB0 = ETA(7) ;ZTG = ETA(8) ;ZTS = ETA(9) TLIM = THETA(34) * EXP(ZTLIM) ; shrinkage pleateau ENDIF
; Covariate effects parameters ; treatment, treatment line, albumin, Karnofsky Performance Status, number of lesions, and PDL-1 status
; albumin on TB0 and TG TB0ALB = THETA(14) TGALB = THETA(15)
; treatment on TG and TS TGCOMB = THETA(16) TGPLB = THETA(17)
TSCOMB = THETA(18) TSPLB = THETA(19)
; therapy line on TG and TS TG2L = THETA(20) TS2L = THETA(21)
; KPS on TB0 and TG ( <=70 as reference) TB0KPS80 = THETA(22) TB0KPS90 = THETA(23) TB0KPS100 = THETA(24)
TGKPS80 = THETA(25) TGKPS90 = THETA(26) TGKPS100 = THETA(27)
; #target lesion on TG and TS TGNTS = THETA(28) TSNTS = THETA(29)
; PD-L1 (5% cutoff) on TG and TS (negative as reference) TGPDL1P = THETA(30) TGPDL1U = THETA(31)
TSPDL1P = THETA(32) TSPDL1U = THETA(33)
; Get identify of most likely sub-pop MEST = MIXEST
; Covariate effects equations
; log-linear albumin effect on TB0 and TG (centered at mean log) TVTB0 = TVTB0 * (1+lcBALB*TB0ALB) TVTG = TVTG * (1+lcBALB*TGALB)
; treatment effect on TG and TS IF(TXAN .EQ. 3) THEN ; TVTS = TVTS * EXP(TSCOMB) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGCOMB) ENDIF IF(TXAN .EQ. 4) THEN ; TVTS = TVTS * EXP(TSPLB) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGPLB) ENDIF
; therapy line effect on TG and TS (>= 2nd line vs. first line) IF(LINEN .GE. 2) THEN TVTS = TVTS * EXP(TS2L) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TG2L) ENDIF
; KPS score on TB0 and TG (>= 2nd line vs. first line) IF(KPSN .EQ. 2) THEN ; KPS 80 TVTB0 = TVTB0 * EXP(TB0KPS80) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGKPS80) ENDIF IF(KPSN .EQ. 3) THEN ; KPS 90 TVTB0 = TVTB0 * EXP(TB0KPS90) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGKPS90) ENDIF IF(KPSN .EQ. 4) THEN ; KPS 100 TVTB0 = TVTB0 * EXP(TB0KPS100) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGKPS100) ENDIF
; #target lesion on TG and TS TVTG = TVTG * (INILSN/2)**TGNTS TVTS = TVTS * (INILSN/2)**TSNTS
; PD-L1 on TG and TS IF(PDL15N .EQ.2) THEN ; positive TVTS = TVTS * EXP(TSPDL1P) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGPDL1P) ENDIF IF(PDL15N .EQ. 3) THEN ; unknown TVTS = TVTS * EXP(TSPDL1U) TVTG = TVTG * EXP(TGPDL1U) ENDIF
; Calculate individual values of TGD model params TB0 = TVTB0*EXP(ZTB0) TG = TVTG*EXP(ZTG) TS = TVTS*EXP(ZTS)
;---- PD TUMOR EFF1 = TB0*EXP(-TS*TIME/7) + TLIM EFF2 = TG*TIME/7 IPRED = (EFF1 + EFF2)
IRES = DV - IPRED
REWT = SQRT(AERR**2 + (PERR**2)*(IPRED**2)) IWRES = IRES/REWT
Y = IPRED + REWT*EPS(1)
$MIX P1 = THETA(12) P2 = THETA(13)
P(1) = P1/(1+P1+P2) P(2) = P2/(1+P1+P2) P(3) = 1/(1+P1+P2)
NSPOP = 3
